Symbol.Script_3D:
!-----------3d--------------------- if show_el < EPS then end if show_op<EPS then end CALL "MEP_m_RequestSystemGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL one_ConID=0 returned_parameters gs_cont_pen, sMat, gs_InsMat, MEP_cline_pen, show_el shadow off material sMat
GROUP "Плита" BLOCK op_B, op_B, op_S1 ENDGROUP
GROUP "Болтовой цилиндр" ADD op_W/2, op_W/2, 0 CYLIND op_S1, op_d/2 DEL 1 ADD op_W/2, op_W/2+op_e, 0 CYLIND op_S1, op_d/2 DEL 1 ADD op_W/2+op_e, op_W/2+op_e, 0 CYLIND op_S1, op_d/2 DEL 1 ADD op_W/2+op_e, op_W/2, 0 CYLIND op_S1, op_d/2 DEL 1 ENDGROUP
GROUP "Патрубок" mulz -1 sc=12 if NSP>0 then tt = max(get(NSP)) RESOL 36 PUT op_B/2,op_B/2,900+sc PUT op_dn/2,360,4000+sc PUT op_dn/2-op_S,360,4000+sc if NSP>0 then PRISM_ NSP/3, op_h1-op_S1, GET(NSP) DEL 1 ENDGROUP
GROUP "Отвод" ADD op_B/2, op_B/2, 0 ROTx 180 ELBOW op_F, op_angle, op_R DEL 1 ENDGROUP
RESULT1=SUBGROUP ("Плита","Болтовой цилиндр") RESULT2=SUBGROUP ("Патрубок","Отвод")
hotspot 0,0,0
HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, op_h1, 1+128+512: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, op_h1, unID, op_h1, 2+512: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, op_h1-1, unID, op_h1, 3+512: unID=unID+1
add -op_B/2, -op_B/2, 0 PLACEGROUP RESULT1 add 0, 0, op_h1 PLACEGROUP RESULT2
PLACEGROUP "Отвод" KILLGROUP "Патрубок" KILLGROUP "Отвод" KILLGROUP RESULT1 KILLGROUP RESULT2 KILLGROUP "Плита" KILLGROUP "Болтовой цилиндр"
